# PayWise AI Agent

## Track
Best Agentic Economy Experience on Arc

## Tagline
An AI Agent That Doesn't Just Advise — It Acts.

## Overview
PayWise AI Agent is an autonomous financial assistant designed to help freelancers, remote workers, and SMEs make smarter cross-border payment decisions using stablecoin infrastructure.

## Problem
Millions of freelancers and remote workers face:

- High international transfer fees
- Slow settlement times
- Limited transparency
- Complex payment decisions

Traditional payment tools only provide information and do not actively help users make the best decision.

## Solution
PayWise AI Agent:

1. Understands payment requests
2. Compares payment routes
3. Evaluates fees and settlement time
4. Explains its recommendation
5. Demonstrates USDC settlement concepts
6. Generates a transaction receipt

## Example

### User Request
Send $500 to Pakistan

### Route Comparison

| Route | Fee | Time |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Bank Wire | $45 | 5-7 Days |
| Western Union | $25 | 2-3 Days |
| USDC | $1 | 5 Minutes |

### Recommendation
USDC is recommended because it provides the lowest cost and fastest settlement.

